Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.22,0:00:04.64,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Do you have many memories from your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.46,0:00:07.58,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Memories? Do you mean records?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:10.42,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Well, memories and records aren’t exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:12.84,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Don't think about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.58,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you’ve traveled somewhere during summer vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.72,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I haven’t traveled anywhere during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:21.86,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:29.24,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,In my youth, both of my parents worked, so I didn’t get to travel very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:35.36,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I didn’t like it when I went back to school after vacation and other kids would ask me where I went or what I did during the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:38.32,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What’s the difference between a memory and a record?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:47.30,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,From a medical standpoint, a record is something documented that lists exactly what happened, when and where.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:49.52,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,A memory is more subjective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:51.30,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It’s what you remember personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:55.72,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It’s something in your mind that you can access from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:59.74,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,But Lain, doesn’t all this stuff bore you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:04.34,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,No. How does a memory enter the brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:11.90,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,How? That’s a pretty complicated subject. Are you sure you want to get into it?